{"tid":1722731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個文宣方面嘅諗法","createTime":"2019-11-15T03:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T06:06:36.000Z","uid":156326,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a65ec5aa90b21ed40bf2e89544b35592c2096bca","tid":1722731,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"其實今時今日 我地淨係煲大二噁英山埃已經夠打民意戰<br />\n<br />\n我覺得依家文宣圖只需要三種templates<br />\n<br />\n第一種就係果張 你行過嘅呢個地區曾經有山埃毒性 但我搵唔番張圖<br />\n<br />\n第二種就係呢張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9rU0Mk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9rU0Mk.png&h=29da4df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三種就係要畸胎嘅樣 最好係你一望到就唔撚舒服果啲想嘔果啲<br />\n<br />\n要令睇到嘅人有以下心路歷程<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定要各區鋪天蓋地咁貼文宣先可以轉移番去政府度 唔使講啲咩民主自由 同佢講你會生癌 個孫會變畸胎仲好<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家推推"},{"pid":"eddec6330f230626190c12a1ce2cc994f3861860","tid":1722731,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:36:36.000Z","msg":"推 推 推 推 推"},{"pid":"341ee3e07dba1162bd78df0b6383d7dbff57f0b2","tid":1722731,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69a20a33814772fd020d92069db5b8e2cdc0fc27","tid":1722731,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:37:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"957557560a5d82ea78082e6206c387d6365e07aa","tid":1722731,"uid":156326